Package: countWords
Type: Package
Title: Return the number of words from a provided dataframe.  
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Keith Albee
Maintainer: Keith Albee <kalbee@usf.edu>
Description: This package will include functions that allow users to find the 
wordcount of dataframes. You can specify which word you want to be counted and
the source content, and it will return a new dataframe with the word and the
number of times it came up. You can also just provide a dataframe to get the
total number of words provided. 
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
License: CC0
LazyData: true
